The '''Barbados Bar Association''' is a voluntary association of [[Attorney at law|attorneys]] in [[Barbados]] who practise at the independent [[Bar association|bar]] as [[barristers]] and [[Queen's Counsel]]. It was created by the Barbados Bar Association Act of 1940.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.barbadosbarassociation.com/about_us.cfm|title=About The Barbados Bar Association|accessdate=26 September 2012}}</ref>
